            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%BA%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E6%9F%A5%E8%A1%80%E8%84%82%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%BA%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E6%9F%A5%E8%A1%80%E8%84%82%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#哪些人需要重点查血脂#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>根据《中国血脂管理指南(2023)》建议，这四类人需要重点查血脂👇🏻<br><br>1⃣️有动脉粥样硬化性心血管疾病病史；<br>2⃣️有高血压、糖尿病、肥胖或吸烟等情况；<br>3⃣️有早发心血管病家族史；<br>4⃣️皮肤有脂黄瘤、腱黄瘤等的胆固醇代谢异常人群。（科普中国）<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcvqs70aogj20gr09kq4u.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
