            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%8E%A7%E7%83%9F%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%97%B6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%8E%A7%E7%83%9F%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%97%B6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳控烟进行时#</span></a> 【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>深圳控烟第3弹现场！南山烟民为避执法将烟藏进衣服！】4月10日上午，由深圳市控烟办、深圳市市场监督管理局南山监管局等工作人员组成的督查组来到南山区南山市场，开展第三场农贸（集贸、批发）市场控烟督查。本次控烟督查执法人员发现2位吸烟市民，进行了宣教和处罚。竟有烟民为躲执法人员，将未灭烟头藏进衣服里<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>快和小卫一起看现场👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E5%86%85%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%9D%E8%A7%84%E5%90%B8%E7%83%9F%E8%A2%AB%E7%BD%9A%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E5%86%85%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%9D%E8%A7%84%E5%90%B8%E7%83%9F%E8%A2%AB%E7%BD%9A%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳一市场内多人违规吸烟被罚#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87V%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87V%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升V计划#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4889353114288220" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/